    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering an ideal balance of mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This automobile has been curated to meet the expectations of the discerning driver, featuring a robust powertrain and a well-preserved interior. It represents a significant value proposition for those seeking a reliable, high-performance vehicle without the premium of a showroom-floor price tag. We invite you to experience the superior handling and enduring quality of this exceptional motorcar.",
      "price": 31500.0,
